org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Brokering

Interface DeviceBroker

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SwResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeviceBrokerImpl

    public interface DeviceBroker
extends SwResource
    A representation of the model object 'Device Broker'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Access Policy
    • Is Buffered
    • Devices
    • Close Services
    • Control Services
    • Open Services
    • Read Services
    • Write Services
    See Also:
    SW_BrokeringPackage.getDeviceBroker()
